{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cardinal Descent is an addictively complex roguelike deckbuilder where you play element based hands against powerful enemies, create your own rules and discover outrageous synergies. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Master the Elements</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Strategically play element based cards to pull off combos of your choosing. With over 50 sub types of cards within each suit, and over 100 game changing Space Cards.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/extras/master-the-elements.gif?t=1739075443\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Change the Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every rule of each element is controlled by a card, meaning you can change exactly how each each suit behaves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/extras/change_the_game.gif?t=1739075443\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Break The Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock cards over multiple runs and strategically build your deck around specific strategies to maximize your abilities and pull off absurd combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/extras/break_the_game.gif?t=1739075443\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Uncover the Mystery</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you unlock more cards, more is revealed about why you are playing, how you got here and who you are. With a story adapted from the 12 Labours of Hercules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/extras/uncover_the_mystery.gif?t=1739075443\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114100/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739075443","background_raw"